  "name": "Nimbus of Light",
  "type": "feat",
  "img": "systems/pf1/icons/spells/light-royal-2.jpg",
  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>At 8th level, you can emit a 30-foot nimbus of light for a number of rounds per day equal to your cleric level. This acts as a @Compendium[pf1.spells.7x2z0i8rcx7s81fk]{Daylight} spell. In addition, undead within this radius take an amount of damage equal to your cleric level each round that they remain inside the nimbus. Spells and spell-like abilities with the darkness descriptor are automatically dispelled if brought inside this nimbus. These rounds do not need to be consecutive.</p>",
